title: Chanel Coco Charm Tote Bag
description: Chanel Coco Charm shopping tote bag in black diamond quilted lambskin leather and smooth leather on sides (#23xxxxxx: 2016-2017). Featuring antique silver-toned hardware, dual leather-chain woven shoulder straps, and a interlocking CC charm at front. The top zipper opens to a black textile-lined spacious compartment with a zip pocket. Approximate dimensions: 32cm(Base-L) x 25.5cm(H) x 12cm(D), and 25.5cm shoulder drop. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned).
